Write a program to print a solid diamond pattern of 2N - 1 rows using the asterisk character (*).

ANS;;---
n = int(input())

k = n - 1
for i in range(1, n+1):
    spaces = " " * k
    stars = "* " * i
    print(spaces+stars)
    k = k - 1

k = n
for i in range(1, n):
    spaces = " " * i
    stars = "* " * (k - i)
    print(spaces+stars)

